sellerAgent.name: Jody DuPont GRI MCNE COMPASS360 CO-BROKER

data.description: This Beautiful Traditional 2 Story, Waterfront Property has so much to offer! The home opens to the foyer flanked with formal living or office space on one side and formal dining on the other. Straight ahead is a spacious living area complete with a beautiful fireplace, wood ceiling beams, built-in cabinetry, and large windows and double glass doors that both overlook the lake and lead to the enclosed sunroom. The kitchen is complete with lots of cabinetry and a breakfast area with large windows overlooking the lake. The laundry and 1/2 bath are off of the kitchen as well as the exit to the 2 car garage. The Large Primary Suite is downstairs with his/her closets, double sinks a separate dressing area, tiled shower and separate standard tub. Take the beautiful wide staircase upstairs to find 2 additional bedrooms and 1 full bath with double sinks and tub/shower combo. Back downstairs to the large enclosed sunroom, imagine enjoying beautiful sunsets over the lake. Potential is endless! Directions: US 1/State Street Northbound, turn right onto Wacona Drive; proceed until Frontier Estates and left onto Bland Road, first road up to the right is Frontier Drive, then left on to Winchester, home will be down on the left.
